description:
The package.json file has two 'dependencies' fields (lines 16-20 and 21-23), which is invalid JSON. The second one overwrites the first in parsers but should be merged into a single dependencies field.

Current:
  "dependencies": {
    "next": "15.3.1",
    "react": "^19.1.0",
    "react-dom": "^19.1.0"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "tailwind-merge": "^6.0.0"
  },

Should be:
  "dependencies": {
    "next": "15.3.1",
    "react": "^19.1.0",
    "react-dom": "^19.1.0",
    "tailwind-merge": "^6.0.0"
  },

The tsconfig.json file extends './tsconfig.json' which creates a circular reference. Should extend the base tsconfig from the monorepo root.

Current:
{
  "extends": "./tsconfig.json",
  "compilerOptions": {
    "jsx": "preserve",
    "noEmit": true
  },
  "include": [
    "app/**/*",
    "components/**/*",
    "lib/**/*",
    "types/**/*",
    "utils/**/*"
  ]
}

Should be changed to extend the root tsconfig.base.json:
{
  "extends": "../tsconfig.base.json",
  "compilerOptions": {
    "jsx": "preserve",
    "noEmit": true
  },
  "include": [
    "app/**/*",
    "components/**/*",
    "lib/**/*",
    "types/**/*",
    "utils/**/*"
  ]
}

The next.config.js file contains 'experimental: { appDir: true }' which is deprecated in Next.js 13+ as the app router is now stable. This should be removed to avoid warnings.

Current config:
/** @type {import('next').NextConfig} */
const nextConfig = {
  experimental: {
    appDir: true,
  },
}

Should be changed to:
/** @type {import('next').NextConfig} */
const nextConfig = {}

(or keep other config if present)

The tailwind.config.js file uses Tailwind v3 format but the project has tailwindcss@^4.1.0 installed. Need to update to Tailwind v4 configuration format which requires a 'content' array specifying template paths.

Current content:
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  darkMode: ['class'],
  theme: {
    extend: {}
  },
  plugins: [],
}

Should be updated to:
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  darkMode: ['class'],
  content: [
    './app/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}',
    './components/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}',
    './lib/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}',
    './utils/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}'
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {}
  },
  plugins: [],
}
